### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@userId = {{userId}}

### 1. Đăng ký user mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nguyenvana@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenDayDu": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
  "phongBanId": null,
  "chucVuId": null,
  "ngaySinh": "1990-01-01",
  "ngayVaoLam": "2024-01-01"
}

### 2. Lấy danh sách users (tất cả)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Users?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### 3. Tìm kiếm users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Users?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=nguyen

### 4. Lấy chi tiết user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Users/{{userId}}

### 5. Cập nhật user
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenDayDu": "Nguyễn Văn A - Updated",
  "phoneNumber": "0987654321",
  "phongBanId": null,
  "chucVuId": null,
  "ngaySinh": "1990-01-01",
  "ngayVaoLam": "2024-01-01",
  "status": "Active"
}

### 6. Xóa user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Users/{{userId}}

